This directory contains some unit tests for Ray.


# To run unit tests

bash main.sh


# To add a unit test

Add a file named test_<test_name>.sh

main.sh will pick it up.

Report failed tests and number of passed tests possibly.


# Blackbox unit tests

C++ files for unit tests should be in this directory, not inside the class files to be tested.


# Data for unit tests

The directory data-for-unit-tests contains data for unit tests.
data-for-unit-tests is a symbolic link as data-for-unit-tests content is not
in the git repository.

Send an email to denovoassembler-devel AT lists.sourceforge.net to get it.


